## Write a program to convert paise to rupees

```txt
Input  ( Ps ) : 100
Output ( Rs ) : 1
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="convert-paise-to-rupees" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    float paise, rupee;
    scanf("%f", &paise);
    rupee = paise / 100;
    printf("%.2f", rupee);
    return 0;
}
```

